file_content.text: Where is Darth Vowrawn?
You'll never find out, scum.
You defeated Lord Haresh, but you can't overcome the three of us at once....
Stop. Lord Qet, stand down.
My lord, retreat into the shadows. We will stop this assassin.
There could be ten of you and you would fail. Leave us.
Listen to your master, Qet.
You heard him.
Thank you for sparing them. They will not be a problem for you or your master.
You've all got it wrong.
Please. Don't insult my intelligence.
I don't care if they're here.
They can stay.
Spare them. They pose no threat to you or your master.
I applaud you. Convey my congratulations to your master for his superior game play.
At least I die at Sith Blood hands. I ask only that I not suffer the indignity of decapitation.
The kill is yours. I ask only that I not suffer the indignity of decapitation.
The last thing I want is your death.
I am your ally, Vowrawn.
Start paying attention or I will take your head.
Use your ears and listen.
I've been sent by the Emperor's Hands to ensure your safety.
I am an agent of the Emperor.
Baras is not my master. My mission is to bring him down.
Nothing more can be gained by maintaining the deception....
Ah, if this is true, the game is renewed!
Darth Vowrawn, Baras says you gotta die.
Baras strikes!
The bounty on your head is dead or dead.
Target, Darth Vowrawn, confirmed. Baras directive one initiated. Death.
